{"id":606456,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/02/【立此存照】暗藏包子维尼：游戏《还愿/","date":"2019-02-23T11:29:44Z","modified":"2019-02-25T10:25:29Z","title":"【立此存照】暗藏“包子”“维尼”：游戏《还愿》一夜之间从“国产之光”到“伤害感情”","content":"<p><strong>【编者注】</strong>近日刚发行的台湾独立游戏《还愿》，最初在中国大陆用户间饱受好评；然而仅一天后，有网民发现该游戏似乎隐藏了一些讽刺中共体制及其领导人的元素，比如游戏背景画面中有疑似辱骂习近平的内容，还有诸如“包子被判三年以上最高死刑”、<br />\n“袭击小学童 包子被逮捕 犯人自称萝莉控”这样容易让人联想到习近平的“新闻标题”。与此同时，该游戏中的一个关键“邪教组织”名为陆心社，也因此被部分大陆网民认为是在讽刺中共。</p>\n<p>截至发稿时，<strong>该新浪微博已对“还愿”一词进行了隐蔽的审查，包含该词的内容被自动限制为只有发布者可见。中国大陆的视频网站已全面删除并屏蔽了相关游戏实况，<a href=\"https://webcache.googleusercontent.com/search?q=cache:nYE5mAGmRNMJ:https://www.gcores.com/articles/105552+\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">相关报道</a>在游戏网站上消失，不少论坛也声明将禁止用户讨论《还愿》及其制作者赤烛游戏。</strong>赤烛官方微博 <a href=\"https://www.weibo.com/redcandlegames\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">@赤燭遊戲</a> 所有内容被锁定，无法进行任何转发或评论，很可能已遭炸号。新浪微博经常会保留被销号用户的<del>“尸体”</del>内容，使这些账号表面看起来似乎只是停止更新。</p>\n<p>另外，有大量疑似中国大陆玩家在游戏平台 Steam 给《还愿》以及同样是由赤烛发行的《返校》游戏页面下<a href=\"https://www.reddit.com/r/Games/comments/atrybi/devotion_taiwan_topselling_indie_horror_on_steam/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">打出数千差评</a>。</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p class=\"title\"><strong>相关阅读：<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2019/02/%E5%BE%B7%E5%9B%BD%E4%B9%8B%E5%A3%B0-%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E6%9A%97%E8%AF%AD%E5%BC%95%E5%B7%AE%E8%AF%84-%E6%81%90%E6%80%96%E6%B8%B8%E6%88%8F%E3%80%8A%E8%BF%98%E6%84%BF%E3%80%8B%E9%94%80%E9%87%8F/\">德国之声 | 政治暗语引差评 恐怖游戏《还愿》销量逆势成长</a></strong></p>\n</blockquote>\n<p><strong>以下图片均来自网络：</strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_606460\" style=\"width: 460px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/还愿反革命.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-606460\" class=\"wp-image-606460\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/还愿反革命.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"214\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/还愿反革命.jpg 501w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/还愿反革命-300x143.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-606460\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">微博截图</span></p></div>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/006iH5Dmly1g0g7sj2uk1j30ku112wh6.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-606454\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/006iH5Dmly1g0g7sj2uk1j30ku112wh6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"712\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/006iH5Dmly1g0g7sj2uk1j30ku112wh6.jpg 440w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/006iH5Dmly1g0g7sj2uk1j30ku112wh6-169x300.jpg 169w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/WsTJ7CQ.png\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-606453\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/WsTJ7CQ.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"348\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/WsTJ7CQ.png 640w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/WsTJ7CQ-300x261.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p>咒符中的印章赫然显示“小熊维尼习近平”：</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_606450\" style=\"width: 410px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/KxKM5px-e1550916775116.png\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-606450\" class=\"wp-image-606450\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/KxKM5px-e1550916775116.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"341\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/KxKM5px-e1550916775116.png 450w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/KxKM5px-e1550916775116-300x256.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-606450\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">“小熊维尼习近平”</span></p></div>\n<p>游戏背景中的一张旧报纸也被网民找了出来：</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_606443\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/006pFK4Lly1g0ggida4f4j30k00q3jy3.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-606443\" class=\"wp-image-606443\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/006pFK4Lly1g0ggida4f4j30k00q3jy3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"652\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/006pFK4Lly1g0ggida4f4j30k00q3jy3.jpg 720w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/006pFK4Lly1g0ggida4f4j30k00q3jy3-230x300.jpg 230w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-606443\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">“包子被判三年以上最高死刑” </span><br /><span style=\"color: #808080\">“袭击小学童 包子被逮捕 犯人自称萝莉控”</span></p></div>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/JMbzwoq.png\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-606449\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/JMbzwoq.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"801\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/JMbzwoq.png 666w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/JMbzwoq-150x300.png 150w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/JMbzwoq-511x1024.png 511w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p>有大陆网民向迪士尼中国投诉，认为《还愿》将“维尼熊”写在咒符上是“盗取知识产权”：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/SMPQOYw.png\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-606451\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/SMPQOYw.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"866\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/SMPQOYw.png 616w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/SMPQOYw-139x300.png 139w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/SMPQOYw-473x1024.png 473w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p>赤烛游戏称这一切“实属意外”，并已将咒符中的“小熊维尼习近平”改为了“恭贺新禧”：</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_606447\" style=\"width: 410px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/c4CKSoM.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-606447\" class=\"wp-image-606447\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/c4CKSoM.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"418\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/c4CKSoM.jpg 1080w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/c4CKSoM-287x300.jpg 287w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/c4CKSoM-768x802.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/c4CKSoM-980x1024.jpg 980w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-606447\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">赤烛游戏Facebook声明截图</span></p></div>\n<p>该游戏大陆代理商 Indievent 于2月23日发表声明，称因更新后的游戏中仍存有“隐喻政治元素”，将正式终止与赤烛的合作关系：<br />\n<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/52823406_1180208738808334_5318764594582257664_n.png\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-606445\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/52823406_1180208738808334_5318764594582257664_n.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"502\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/52823406_1180208738808334_5318764594582257664_n.png 690w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/52823406_1180208738808334_5318764594582257664_n-239x300.png 239w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p>所有相关游戏视频在中国大陆被全面撤下：</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/3RropJq.png\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-606441\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/3RropJq.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"522\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/3RropJq.png 529w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/3RropJq-230x300.png 230w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/yUwhztd.png\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-606459\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/yUwhztd.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"52\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/yUwhztd.png 947w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/yUwhztd-300x31.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/yUwhztd-768x79.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a> <a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/还愿.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-606458\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/还愿.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"540\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/还愿.jpg 1004w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/还愿-222x300.jpg 222w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/还愿-768x1037.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/还愿-758x1024.jpg 758w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_606448\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/e3915816.jpg\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-606448\" class=\"wp-image-606448\" src=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/e3915816.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"362\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/e3915816.jpg 851w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/e3915816-300x217.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2019/02/e3915816-768x556.jpg 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p id=\"caption-attachment-606448\" class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080\">盗版游戏论坛3DM创办人宿菲菲怒斥赤烛“狼子野心的畜生”</span></p></div>\n","author":980,"categories":[18270,18269,19168,10466,27949],"tags":[10218,25995,18816,8639,10268,33491,23155,38055,38056]}